# Incident: Tableau Reports ABBVIE Certifications - Not On Reports
***

*** 
## Incident Details

- **Incident Date:** 2026-02-16 15:27:00  
- **Reported By:** TAA Business Team  
- **Impacted System:** Tableau  
- **Severity:** Low  
- **Status:** Resolved  
***

***
## Incident Description

Team ABBVIE 0110 certifications for 2-12-2026 were not showing on the All Product or the FSSCOOWeeklyChange reports.
***

***
## Business Impact

- Dashboards showed incorrect metrics
- Daily operational reviews were delayed
- Manual verification was required by analysts

***

***
## Root Cause Analysis

- The script was not updated to fulfill the necessary ask from the business user.

***

***
## Resolution

- Updated Tableau scripts to obtain the required data columns and modify the tableau reports accordingly.
- Validated dashboards against source data
***

***

## Preventive Measures

- Add schema validation checks before refresh
- Add validation checks after every production deployment.

